{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"nonisolated"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"labelsVisibility"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"_"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"visibility"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Visibility","text":"Visibility","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore10VisibilityO"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","text":"View","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP"},{"kind":"text","text":"\n"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this modifier when you want to omit a label from one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"labeled content in your user interface. For example, the first "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Toggle"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in the following example hides its label:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["VStack {","    Toggle(isOn: $toggle1) {","        Text(\"Toggle 1\")","    }","    .labelsVisibility(.hidden)","","    Toggle(isOn: $toggle2) {","        Text(\"Toggle 2\")","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/VStack"},{"text":" in the example above centers the first toggle’s control","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"element in the available space, while it centers the second toggle’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"combined label and control element:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Always provide a label for controls, even when you hide the label,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"because OpenSwiftUI uses labels for other purposes, including accessibility.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"On iOS, a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Picker"},{"type":"text","text":" within a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Menu"},{"type":"text","text":" hides its label by default. You can use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this modifier to explicitly show the label in that context:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["Menu {","    Picker(\"Flavor\", selection: $selectedFlavor) {","        Text(\"Chocolate\").tag(Flavor.chocolate)","        Text(\"Vanilla\").tag(Flavor.vanilla)","        Text(\"Strawberry\").tag(Flavor.strawberry)","    }","    .labelsVisibility(.visible)","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"aside","name":"Note","style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This modifier doesn’t work for all labels. It applies to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/LabeledContent","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" elements, including controls like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Picker"},{"type":"text","text":" and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Toggle","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":", but not to controls like a bordered button where the label"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is inside the button’s border."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Controls the visibility of labels of any controls contained within this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AnyView"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AnyView\/labelsVisibility(_:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"platforms":[{"unavailable":false,"name":"iOS","introducedAt":"13.0","beta":false,"deprecated":false},{"unavailable":false,"name":"macOS","introducedAt":"10.15","beta":false,"deprecated":false},{"unavailable":false,"name":"tvOS","introducedAt":"13.0","beta":false,"deprecated":false},{"unavailable":false,"name":"visionOS","introducedAt":"1.0","beta":false,"deprecated":false},{"unavailable":false,"name":"watchOS","introducedAt":"6.0","beta":false,"deprecated":false}],"symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"OpenSwiftUI","relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"]}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"LabelVisibility.swift","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUI\/View\/LabelContent\/LabelVisibility.swift#L60"},"fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"labelsVisibility","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"Visibility","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore10VisibilityO","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"View","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP0aB2UIE16labelsVisibilityyQrAA0G0OF::SYNTHESIZED::s:15OpenSwiftUICore7AnyViewV","roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"labelsVisibility(_:)","extendedModule":"OpenSwiftUICore"},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/anyview\/labelsvisibility(_:)"]}],"references":{"doc://OpenSwi